constructor(tuple(address endpoint, bytes config)[] _plugins, address _wEth) payable
event MultiplierExecuted(address indexed user, address indexed comet, address indexed collateral, uint256 multipliedAmount, uint256 debt)
event MultiplierWithdrawn(address indexed user, address indexed comet, address indexed collateral, uint256 withdrawnAmount, uint256 amountOut)
event PluginAdded(address indexed endpoint, bytes4 indexed selector, bytes32 key)
function executeMultiplier(tuple(address comet, address loanPlugin, address swapPlugin) opts, address collateral, uint256 collateralAmount, uint256 leverage, bytes swapData) payable

function executeMultiplierBySig(tuple(address comet, address loanPlugin, address swapPlugin) opts, address collateral, uint256 collateralAmount, uint256 leverage, bytes swapData, tuple(uint256 nonce, uint256 expiry, bytes32 r, bytes32 s, uint8 v) allowParams) payable
function withdrawMultiplier(tuple(address comet, address loanPlugin, address swapPlugin) opts, address collateral, uint256 collateralAmount, bytes swapData)

function withdrawMultiplierBySig(tuple(address comet, address loanPlugin, address swapPlugin) opts, address collateral, uint256 collateralAmount, bytes swapData, tuple(uint256 nonce, uint256 expiry, bytes32 r, bytes32 s, uint8 v) allowParams)
